@startuml
!theme blueprint
title Level-0 DFD - NMEA Parser Context Diagram

actor "GPS Device" as GPS
actor "User Application" as App

rectangle "NMEA Parser System" as Parser {
    note top of Parser : Provides a POSIX-like interface\n(open/close/read/write)
}

GPS --> Parser : NMEA Sentences
Parser --> App : Parsed Data (Raw or JSON)
App --> Parser : Control Commands / Configurations
@enduml